if exists(select 1 from sys.sysforeignkey where role='FK_MPS_OPST_ADMINSTRA_MPS_NASE') then
alter table MPS_OPSTINA
delete foreign key FK_MPS_OPST_ADMINSTRA_MPS_NASE
end if;

alter table MPS_OPSTINA
add constraint FK_MPS_OPST_ADMINSTRA_MPS_NASE foreign key (MPS_DR_IDENTIFIKATOR, NM_DENTIFIKATOR)
references MPS_NASELJENO_MESTO (DR_IDENTIFIKATOR, NM_DENTIFIKATOR)
on update restrict
on delete restrict;
